OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776712271
OL,3,CHairy Biker Dave Myers to be
OL,4,Cremembered with 'last ride home'
OL,6,FThe massive charity bike ride from
OL,7,FLondon to Cumbria in memory of Hairy
OL,8,FBiker Dave Myers will return for a
OL,9,Fthird - and likely final - year this
OL,10,FJune.
OL,12,FDubbed 'Dave Day: The Last Ride Home,'
OL,13,Fthe event will see tens of thousands
OL,14,Fof bikers travel from the capital to
OL,15,Fthe TV chef's hometown of Barrow to
OL,16,Fraise funds for Childline and other
OL,17,Fcauses that were close to his heart.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
