OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776712271
OL,3,CHairy Biker Dave Myers to be
OL,4,Cremembered with 'last ride home'
OL,6,FDave, one half of the beloved Hairy
OL,7,FBikers duo alongside Si King, died in
OL,8,F2024 at the age of 66 after being
OL,9,Fdiagnosed with cancer.
OL,11,FOrganiser Jason Woodcock, a close
OL,12,Ffriend of the late star, confirmed
OL,13,Fthat while the 2026 ride-out is going
OL,14,Fahead on 20 June, it will be the last
OL,15,Fof its kind due to significant
OL,16,Ffinancial challenges.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776712271
OL,3,CHairy Biker Dave Myers to be
OL,4,Cremembered with 'last ride home'
OL,6,FThe future of the event had been in
OL,7,Fdoubt until recently, with Jason
OL,8,Frevealing on social media that
OL,9,FWestmorland and Furness Council could
OL,10,Fnot fund the procession on the same
OL,11,Fscale as previous years.
OL,13,FHe explained that the organisers and
OL,14,FDave's widow Liliana Orzac were asked
OL,15,Fto take on costs ranging "between
OL,16,F#80,000 and #100,000", a figure he
OL,17,Fdescribed as impossible to meet.
OL,19,FAs a result, this year's event will go
OL,20,F"back to basics."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
