FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776712271
OL,3,CHairy Biker Dave Myers to be
OL,4,Cremembered with 'last ride home'
OL,6,F"The only reason I ever got involved
OL,7,Fwith this is because Dave was my mate
OL,8,Fand Dave Day is all about remembering
OL,9,FDave," Jason said in a video on social
OL,10,Fmedia.
OL,12,F"Dave Day is about raising money for
OL,13,FChildline and other charities,
OL,14,Fremembering my mate, and bikers
OL,15,Fgetting together and remembering our
OL,16,Fown lost loves and family."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
