FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776712271
OL,3,CHairy Biker Dave Myers to be
OL,4,Cremembered with 'last ride home'
OL,6,FHe has now called on the community to
OL,7,Fhelp make this the biggest event yet
OL,8,Fand, while the ride remains the
OL,9,Fcentral focus, Jason emphasised that
OL,10,Fmany of charity events are being
OL,11,Forganised independently.
OL,13,F"If you haven't done it yet, this is
OL,14,Fthe one to get on," Jason added.
OL,15,F"Let's make this as big as the first
OL,16,Fone. It's the last big ride up the
OL,17,Fcountry to remember Dave Myers, my
OL,18,Fmate, and the fantastic part of the
OL,19,FHairy Bikers."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
